OL,3,CWhy has Mary Poppins' UK age rating
OL,4,Cbeen raised?
OL,6,FA BBFC spokesperson added: "We only
OL,7,Freview (and potentially reclassify)
OL,8,Fpreviously classified content when
OL,9,Fit's been formally resubmitted to us.
OL,11,F"There are different scenarios in
OL,12,Fwhich content may be resubmitted to us
OL,13,Fby a distributor.
OL,15,F"For example, this could be ahead of
OL,16,Fan upcoming cinema re-release, or a
OL,17,Fnew release on DVD, Blu-ray or other
OL,18,Fhome entertainment formats."
