OL,3,CWhy has Mary Poppins' UK age rating
OL,4,Cbeen raised?
OL,6,FThe BBFC has historically lowered more
OL,7,Fratings than raise them.
OL,9,FBrad Pitt's Fight Club was downgraded
OL,10,Ffrom an 18 rating to 15 despite its
OL,11,Fportrayal of "sequences of graphic and
OL,12,Fbrutal violence".
OL,14,FBut there are cases were ratings have
OL,15,Fbeen raised, such as Pixar's
OL,16,FRatatouille, which was reclassified by
OL,17,Fthe BBFC from a U to a PG rating due
OL,18,Fto instances of "comic violence" and
OL,19,F"mild bad language".
