OL,3,CWhy has Mary Poppins' UK age rating
OL,4,Cbeen raised?
OL,6,FDinosaur thriller Jurassic Park,
OL,7,Fpreviously rated PG, was reclassified
OL,8,Fto 12A last year for "moderate threat,
OL,9,Fviolence, bloody images."
OL,11,FJack Black-led comedy School of Rock,
OL,12,Falso originally rated PG, was raised
OL,13,Fto 12A in 2023 for "moderate bad
OL,14,Flanguage, discriminatory terms, rude
OL,15,Fhumour."
